clock for Debian
================

This is a simple Qt-based desktop clock application.

Build instructions:
  dpkg-buildpackage -us -uc -b

Qt6 / Qt5 compatibility:
  The package prefers Qt6. To build with Qt5, install qtbase5-dev
  and qtbase5-dev-tools instead.

